                "description": {
                    "value": "<p data-visibility=\"gm\"><strong>Requirements</strong> The mandragora has a creature @Compendium[pf2e.conditionitems.Grabbed]{Grabbed};</p>\n<p><strong>Effect</strong> The mandragora drains blood from the creature it has grabbed, dealing [[/r 1d6 #damage]]{1d6 damage}.<span data-visibility=\"gm\"> If the creature is a demon, fey, or sorcerer, the mandragora gains temporary Hit Points equal to the damage dealt.</span> A creature that has its blood drained by a mandragora is @Compendium[pf2e.conditionitems.Drained]{Drained 1} until it receives healing of any kind or amount.</p>"
