                "description": {
                    "value": "<p data-visibility=\"gm\"><strong>Frequency</strong> once per day;</p>\n<p><strong>Effect</strong> The mandragora emits an unsettling shriek. Each non-mandragora creature within 30 feet must attempt a <span data-pf2-check=\"will\" data-pf2-dc=\"20\" data-pf2-traits=\"auditory,evocation,mental,primal\" data-pf2-label=\"Piercing Shriek DC\" data-pf2-show-dc=\"gm\">Will</span> save.</p>\n<div data-visibility=\"gm\">\n<p><strong>Critical Success</strong> The creature is unaffected.</p>\n<p><strong>Success</strong> The creature is @Compendium[pf2e.conditionitems.Sickened]{Sickened 1}.</p>\n<p><strong>Failure</strong> The creature is @Compendium[pf2e.conditionitems.Sickened]{Sickened 2}.</p>\n<p><strong>Critical Failure</strong> The creature is sickened 2 and @Compendium[pf2e.conditionitems.Slowed]{Slowed 1}. As long as the creature remains sickened, this slowed condition value can't be reduced below 1.</p>\n</div>"
